{"tid":1367722,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好再幫襯堅尼地城大新五金","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:11:10.000Z","uid":112076,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4ca113971d5db191eb9854a08d0f505e1c6832","tid":1367722,"uid":112076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好再幫襯堅尼地城大新五金<br />\n<br />\n呢間大新五金嘅老闆用高幾倍嘅價錢賣頭盔比班後生仔<br />\n<br />\n有人問老細做咩賣咁貴 <br />\n<br />\n佢就話佢地有錢就梗係賣貴啲<br />\n<br />\n請各位唔好再幫襯呢間垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/850bdOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F850bdOW.png&h=30af3386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望老細你而家抬高個價 <br />\n祝你而家百病纏身 老時住嘅地方都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細比你睇到大嘅街坊上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a72f83391c79af86f2e097fab8ac65138f8fc4","tid":1367722,"uid":36298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"以後即刻唔買"},{"pid":"0e5cdaa1702ae484bc117a306e9da881133237ec","tid":1367722,"uid":112076,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"大家要認住呢間野 唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別係住係堅城嘅hku仔 <br />\n<br />\n寧願買貴啲都唔好比佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6f38d7b9244aa4ea0c2a62f6e7c572537ce24e","tid":1367722,"uid":112076,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"最最最重要係佢賣嘅全部都只係安全帽 <br />\n<br />\n連個芯都無 <br />\n<br />\n最好買啲有心嘅包得好啲嘅頭盔<br />\n<br />\n發夢比人打都可以防震<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9787b42e983c8104c949961a39a7199f77bced7","tid":1367722,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"幾錢頂？"},{"pid":"77fa7629542485e72381f817dbe70c7d0c2dd248","tid":1367722,"uid":112076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9787b42e983c8104c949961a39a7199f77bced7","tid":1367722,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"幾錢頂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"唔exactly知幾錢<br />\n<br />\n但本身廿幾三廿蚊個<br />\n<br />\n而家高幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225f363a2b29499fa7a1850b726257ce94301202","tid":1367722,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"有啲地方因爲租金高做到50蚊頂 <br />\n小心屌錯人"},{"pid":"306e149586ce8470024539121199d4922f800e4a","tid":1367722,"uid":180317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bae8cfd5f309534d6ad5d7c425d0c314b545afc6","tid":1367722,"uid":213115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74745eec7ecf1cce85c6e22cc52cdc71a42497e8","tid":1367722,"uid":112076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"225f363a2b29499fa7a1850b726257ce94301202","tid":1367722,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"有啲地方因爲租金高做到50蚊頂 <br />\n小心屌錯人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"咁會唔會呢幾日先嚟高幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會唔會係淨係常客先原本嘅價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9729a21f088b1a7c74ddb3ffee2545774fea8d0","tid":1367722,"uid":214635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182ed3538ba2cf97337314e8529c5169a37f3865","tid":1367722,"uid":272010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:54:46.000Z","